{"tid":329253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【外國黑警】警察插贜嫁禍放毒品 隨身攝錄機影低晒","createTime":"2017-07-20T08:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T08:24:59.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03a3c33aed98e25cc570a2c785e148cee3497f88","tid":329253,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T08:24:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170720/56978942\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170720%2F56978942&d=8LRx0u3ywii7NK47kZIC5ywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=26ec087e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170720%2F56978942&h=b02132bc\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170720/56978942</a>入面有片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170720/large/1500533254_e0ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170720%2Flarge%2F1500533254_e0ef.jpg&h=21a6ad48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國馬里蘭州有三名警員涉嫌插贜嫁禍，警員在一個垃圾堆中放下毒品，其後再假扮搜查，一名男子因而被捕。事發經過由警員的隨身攝錄機拍下，事件公開後備受評擊。<br />\n<br />\n90秒的片段中，開首的30秒沒有聲音。從影片看到，一名警員將物品放在一個垃圾堆中，他和在旁的兩名警員其後走開。<br />\n其後警員開啟攝影機的錄音功能，警員說「我正要檢查此處」，其他警員聽畢發笑。警員在垃圾堆中翻查，發現一個罐中藏有毒品。<br />\n當地傳媒報道，一名男子因影片的毒品被捕，他因未能繳交5萬美元(39萬港元)保釋金，由1月被關柙，其後他的控罪被撤銷。警方指正調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n英國《都巿報》  <br />\n<br />\n有冇咁ON9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}